#!/usr/bin/env testml


*jsc.validate(*json) == *valid


=== Test 1 - validation of internationalized host names - a valid host name (example.test in Hangul)
--- valid: true
--- jsc
{"format": "idn-hostname"}
--- json
"실례.테스트"


=== Test 2 - validation of internationalized host names - illegal first char U+302E Hangul single dot tone mark
--- valid: false
--- ^jsc
--- json
"〮실례.테스트"


=== Test 3 - validation of internationalized host names - contains illegal char U+302E Hangul single dot tone mark
--- valid: false
--- ^jsc
--- json
"실〮례.테스트"


